risk measures, for all different
courses of action we consider.

177
00:12:26.260 --> 00:12:29.100
Finally, we will use
optimization tool kit,

178
00:12:29.100 --> 00:12:32.100
to select the best course of action using,
for example,

179
00:12:32.100 --> 00:12:37.520
reward estimate as the objective function,
and risk measures as constraints.

180
00:12:39.220 --> 00:12:43.890
Simulation tool kit is what we're
going to focus on next, and

181
00:12:43.890 --> 00:12:47.110
the process of selecting the best
alternative based on the results of

182
00:12:47.110 --> 00:12:50.310
simulation will be covered next week.

